worker: python bot.py

# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 
# 1. DISCORD BOT SETUP:
#    - Go to https://discord.com/developers/applications
#    - Click "New Application"
#    - Go to "Bot" → Click "Add Bot"
#    - Copy TOKEN from Bot section
#    - Go to OAuth2 → URL Generator
#    - Select scopes: "bot"
#    - Select permissions: "Administrator"
#    - Copy the generated URL and invite bot to your server
#
# 2. RAILWAY DEPLOYMENT:
#    - Go to https://railway.app
#    - Click "New Project" → "Deploy from GitHub"
#    - Select your repository (must be on GitHub)
#    - In "Variables" add: DISCORD_TOKEN = [your_token_from_step_1]
#    - Railway will auto-deploy
#
# 3. VERIFY:
#    - Wait 1-2 minutes
#    - Go to your Discord server
#    - Type "/" and you should see commands: /setup /undo /delete /info
#
# NOTES:
# - Templates auto-create in templates/ folder on first run
# - Examples: gaming.json, community.json, business.json
# - Add your own templates as JSON files in templates/
# - Bot runs 24/7 on Railway (free tier)
#
